      <p><span
          style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:华文细黑;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">14.1&nbsp;【知识产权归属】除非数链科技另行书面声明，</span><span
